returned_payment_fees - NOTE:
Returned payment fees section overstates restrictions. Ala. Admin. Code r. 155-2-4-.12 applies only to deferred presentment transactions. Outside that context, NSF fees may be charged if permitted by contract and other applicable law; they are not limited solely to statute-authorized regimes.

